## Approved Verbs (19 total)
```
Set, Send, Check, Wait for, Clear, Start, Stop
Show, Hide, Add, Remove, Call, Do, Save, Read
Update, Delete, Create, Redirect

Call = specific named things (Call CreateTodo mutation, Call Stripe API)
